Package: qualcoder
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, vlc, ffmpeg
Description: Qualitative Data Analysis Tool
 QualCoder is a free and open-source CAQDAS (Computer Assisted Qualitative
 Data Analysis Software) for coding qualitative data such as text, images,
 and audio/video.
 .
 Features:
  * Code text, images, and multimedia
  * Thematic analysis support
  * Multi-language interface
